Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.83,0:00:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让它陷入了静寂而永恒的睡眠中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.50,0:00:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那个森林即使是现在仍然遍布着坚硬的荆棘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断地阻止着来自外部的侵入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.85,0:00:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 会持续到我死亡的时候为止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.99,0:01:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)}荆棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.98,0:02:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人她…？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.32,0:02:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.09,0:02:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.18,0:02:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试结束后就是圣诞节呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.42,0:02:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄蔷薇大人说结业式时要在蔷薇馆开个联欢会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.69,0:02:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.82,0:02:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.07,0:02:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢圣诞节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要包装吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.17,0:02:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是流言中的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.93,0:02:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是放弃读这本书比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.49,0:02:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.45,0:02:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳怎么想呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我的话 会读的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.10,0:03:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一方面也有些在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先单纯地读读看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.91,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样去读 如果白蔷薇大人的事真写在上面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.67,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.68,0:03:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须加星如果是白蔷薇大人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.95,0:03:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概我会更加尊敬她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会请她在文集上签名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不错啊 你的这种性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.11,0:03:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 果然对是否读这本书犹豫不决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荆棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本书的作者“须加星”实际上是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.06,0:03:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.89,0:03:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 那个白蔷薇大人出版了将自已\n隐藏的过去毫不隐瞒地拼缀起来的自白小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种流言在到处流传
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说也只是流言而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.21,0:03:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些看过这本叫“大波斯菊通信”的\n新刊导读杂志上专题介绍的人们的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荆棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作者 须加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.12,0:04:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学园里数月的生活是否只是梦幻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.28,0:04:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣将一切封印在了心中那荆棘的森林中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.98,0:04:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人期待的新人作家 冲击的自传性处女作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.65,0:04:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须加星与白蔷薇大人的真名“佐藤圣”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确“星”与“圣”发音相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且既然是自传性的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是将自已的过去写在了这本小说里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家会流言四起也是可以理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人过去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.27,0:04:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为一年级生的由乃你们大概不知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.58,0:04:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人的过去也可说是禁忌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.25,0:04:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都尽量不去提及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可说是一种“无言的理解”吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道事情的人大家都三缄其口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像在保护着什么似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是发生了什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.20,0:05:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我是一年级生 没有被告知详细的经过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.26,0:05:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去… 是去年的事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.82,0:05:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.94,0:05:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那个白蔷薇大人的过去写在了这本书里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人会犹豫也是不无道理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.86,0:05:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊 大人们想强制把互为挚友的圣与香织分开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.73,0:05:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是她们在圣诞夜里踏上了没有目的地的旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她们两人想一起死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但当圣在病院里醒过来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香织已经去往天国了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很常见的结局嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.02,0:05:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学 你看到最后都没哭吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.53,0:05:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有些地方和我与祥子大人很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.46,0:05:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 想说的不是小说的内容啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确看了这个后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.58,0:06:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有流言说作者是白蔷薇大人倒也可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小说的舞台只可能是莉莉安啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊 令虽然也看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.26,0:06:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就说“不要再插手这件事”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.14,0:06:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.96,0:06:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“就当没有读过这本小说”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.16,0:06:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“完全不想与流言有任何关联”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.41,0:06:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 祥子大人在买了文集后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉也是对读还是不读犹豫不决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.98,0:06:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令什么也不肯对我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.22,0:06:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 只有直接去问白蔷薇大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.97,0:06:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.61,0:06:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是只有去问白蔷薇大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.26,0:07:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 志摩子同学也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…？ 你们不是姐妹吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不在意吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在就去比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.17,0:07:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.10,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点的话 白蔷薇大人就会去蔷薇馆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.29,0:07:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在令大人与祥子大人面前问不出口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.89,0:07:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年级藤组 佐藤圣同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.17,0:07:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立刻到生活指导室来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是因为那本小说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 佑巳也被传唤了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.68,0:07:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.01,0:07:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是佑巳将我作为“搂抱魔”告发了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.37,0:08:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人 您还不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我本来还想问您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.24,0:08:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“荆棘的森林”的作者\n是否就是白蔷薇大人您或是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.74,0:08:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荆棘？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.83,0:08:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下去的话一会儿再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.56,0:08:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园长 中高等部校长 年级主任以及藤组的负责人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.27,0:08:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“荆棘的森林”已经变成这么严重的问题了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.06,0:08:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人怎么样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是跟往常一样开朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.46,0:08:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好像还不知道被传唤的原因呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.03,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人会怎么样呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.67,0:08:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.74,0:09:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.55,0:09:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是值得告诉新闻部的东西 我们可是一点儿也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说 帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人退学也无所谓吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.54,0:09:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的学园可是禁止打工的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.56,0:09:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写小说什么的明显是违反了校规啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.01,0:09:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退学什么的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.78,0:09:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果事情变成那样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.30,0:09:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用“莉莉安瓦版”来发起署名活动也无所谓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.24,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写上“请不要将白蔷薇大人退学”什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.69,0:09:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我们真的什么也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.72,0:09:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法再支撑下去了 快站好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.16,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 在生活指导室里互相抱着摔在一起可不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.78,0:10:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉打扰到各位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.78,0:10:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.81,0:10:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到\n大家无法抑制的好奇心我还是先报告一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.97,0:10:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 写“荆棘的森林”的人不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.08,0:10:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 这一次不能向\n莉莉安瓦版提供新闻材料真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筑山三奈子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是蔷薇馆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概大家听到传唤的广播后都在等我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当华丽的传唤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.64,0:10:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是从没有因个人的事情而被传唤过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.14,0:10:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有点羡慕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.59,0:10:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是不敢当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是蔷薇大人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没像我这样慌里慌张的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了生活指导室吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.23,0:11:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.16,0:11:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.72,0:11:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.13,0:11:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上等品真是不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我先报告一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.93,0:11:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经向佑巳与由乃说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.03,0:11:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流言中的那本小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.37,0:11:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是被传唤的原因吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.28,0:11:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚地说明不是我写的之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园长为我说了好话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后简单地就让我离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.03,0:11:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自已既没有读过实物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.63,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且对于那个流传的谣言也是刚才才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不是你写的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向圣母玛莉亚发誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个话题就到此结束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.88,0:12:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？ 黄蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.56,0:12:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有异议 红蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 该讨论一下圣诞节的联欢会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.92,0:12:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.17,0:12:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都未受到流言的影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.94,0:12:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真是自我中心又浅薄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.65,0:12:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情低落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.05,0:12:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我脸上的表情又变来变去了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想发言吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.95,0:12:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要睡得迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.96,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见的人要好好地举起手来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.53,0:12:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟会为了这种人而烦恼真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.60,0:13:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手 白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.39,0:13:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 在闹情绪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子 把佑巳借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒是没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.85,0:13:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会脱她的制服或是胡来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.17,0:13:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再开玩笑的话 我可要拒绝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.95,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令 把由乃也借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要由乃愿意的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.64,0:13:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么痛快就允诺没关系吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.94,0:13:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为令明白我不会对由乃淘气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那为什么只对我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为反应很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 祥子的反应也很让人开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.19,0:13:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是一次捉弄就会有双倍乐趣的姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.73,0:13:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.05,0:13:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.03,0:13:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我成了坏心前辈的饵食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 后面的收拾就由我们三人来做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.23,0:14:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家请先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么后面就拜讬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.13,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.53,0:14:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳 不要让白蔷薇大人太开心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.32,0:14:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 有需要我帮忙的事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.82,0:14:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在看起来也没什么需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.87,0:14:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.29,0:14:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们陪着姐姐真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.89,0:14:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.29,0:14:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让志摩子同学跟我们在一起不行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子是那种即使跟她说不要留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要她想留下来就会凭自已的意志留下来的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.25,0:14:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.52,0:14:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.94,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在带着那本“荆棘的森林”吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.12,0:14:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能借我一下吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.69,0:15:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借倒是没什么问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您想做什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.82,0:15:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是读它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.72,0:15:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你以为我会拿它当锅垫吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.53,0:15:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么做为回礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.62,0:15:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面食堂的餐券？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.71,0:15:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.85,0:15:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来的时候在自动贩卖机那里帮我买一罐咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连你们的份也一起买好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.41,0:15:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.42,0:15:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人真是个不可预料的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.12,0:15:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同学真是了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.86,0:15:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟能和那种人做姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.92,0:15:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在颈上围上手帕比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣领会弄脏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.99,0:15:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.79,0:15:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.36,0:15:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人究竟是为了什么将我们留下来呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.69,0:15:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 如果只是为了借“荆棘的森林”的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接带回家去不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.82,0:15:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.21,0:16:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是因为我们太可爱 所以想要请我们吃拉面吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学 脑筋快成豆腐渣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说是不会买罐装年糕豆汤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.98,0:16:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.58,0:16:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？ 那个罐装年糕豆汤什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.57,0:16:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界上还有这种东西存在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.95,0:16:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 白蔷薇大人要的咖啡我们可是好好地买来了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.65,0:16:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经把书仔细地读完了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.65,0:16:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为“荆棘的森林”是我写的\N那些人也许真是有很好的直觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.75,0:16:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不是跟我很像吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.04,0:16:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想问也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.31,0:17:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家会认为写那本小说的是我的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅是名字同音而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点你们也应该有些发觉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.64,0:17:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们毫不掩饰地流露出了那种好奇心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是为了看你们这种表情才说这种话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.52,0:17:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想说的部份我不会说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.38,0:17:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也没问题的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.08,0:17:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为总觉得只有你们不知道不是很不公平吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.76,0:17:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了告诉我们才将我们留下来的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也是为了想早点读到这本书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.96,0:17:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓉子与令她们之所以不向你们说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也许是为了体谅我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那么痛苦的事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾有过一个非常要好的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.22,0:17:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说她甚至比父母和兄弟更加重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.14,0:17:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢她到只要有她在 其它什么也不需要的地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个想着将来成为修女的纯洁的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.71,0:18:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在去年的圣诞节里 她离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.37,0:18:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完完全全是“荆棘的森林”的圣与香织嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.49,0:18:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是完全相同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.25,0:18:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我既没有与那个朋友一起踏上旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.15,0:18:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有吞下安眠药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她转学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.47,0:18:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说香织还活着了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.97,0:18:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 还活着很失望吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.48,0:18:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 难道是谁以白蔷薇大人\N的事作为参考而写下了这本小说吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.87,0:18:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.63,0:18:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既有不同的部份 也有相似得惊人的部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.73,0:18:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得生气吗 白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自已的过去被擅自写成了小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还被人误认为是作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.70,0:18:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 只要能被最重要的人理解就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才想讲给你们俩听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.09,0:19:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我讨厌残留着误解与臆测的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.82,0:19:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转学的朋友 现在怎么样了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.28,0:19:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 怎么样了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.23,0:19:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想见她吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不见面 为好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.86,0:19:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人的名字 不是香织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是久保 栞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.50,0:19:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人现在还喜欢着那个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也这样想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才没有留下志摩子同学吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为会对志摩子同学很过意不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得不可原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.82,0:19:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明会有因小说而受到伤害的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.14,0:19:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写那本小说的不会是久保栞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.17,0:20:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.06,0:20:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.53,0:20:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会彻底查明写这本“荆棘的森林”的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.85,0:20:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是大波斯菊编辑部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要把我也拉来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令也很在意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.05,0:20:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“荆棘的森林”的作者到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.63,0:20:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.06,0:20:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉在忙碌的时候来打扰你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 你是“荆棘的森林”的负责人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是这样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.99,0:20:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我不能将须加星的真实身份告诉你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.44,0:20:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.99,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几天 来自莉莉安学生们的询问接连不断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“须加星的真实身份是否是佐藤圣”之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老…老师！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.43,0:20:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真令人怀念啊 这种制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.11,0:21:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到会在这种地方遇到后辈们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.53,0:21:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.78,0:21:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这么说您是莉莉安的毕业生了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.19,0:21:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是很久以前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.12,0:21:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.93,0:21:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.53,0:21:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是须加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本名是春日诚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.08,0:21:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么“荆棘的森林”的舞台果然是莉莉安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前发生的事情吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.53,0:21:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“荆棘的森林”是在如今\n连传闻都未留下的很久以前发生的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.97,0:21:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟白蔷薇大人的故事就像是其它的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.48,0:21:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有从嘴里说出她的名字了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.31,0:21:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新生吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.14,0:21:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.94,0:22:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今年开始进入莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.48,0:22:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.73,0:23:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 花瓣的瓣是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.03,0:23:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个“瓣”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.62,0:23:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老是拘泥在一些古怪的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.64,0:23:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花瓣的瓣写成汉字就是便当的“便”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.64,0:23:28.34,topfont,NTP,0,0,0,,注：日语中花瓣的“瓣”与便当的“便”同形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.36,0:23:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当的“便”吗 原来如此 是便当的“便”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.45,0:23:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周明明是个好故事 真觉得有点被糟塌啦
